The paper is about automatic program correction using machine learning and deep learning techniques, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. The use of deep generative models and regularizers suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also deals with programming languages (cs.PL) and natural language processing (cs.CL) to some extent.
